Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ 我是州长 我是州长 ♪\N{\fnArial\fs32}♪ I'm the Governor, I'm the Governor! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ 我就是州长 ♪\N{\fnArial\fs32}♪ I'm the Governor! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求你闭嘴好么?\N{\fnArial\fs32}Can you please shut up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在为州长官邸网购90英寸大电视呢\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'm trying to pick out a 90-inch TV for the Governor's mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 Malloy\N{\fnArial\fs32}Whoa, Malloy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的以为你会跟我一起住大官邸啊?\N{\fnArial\fs32}Do you really think you're going to live in the Governor's mansion with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 天真了吧? - 你啥意思?\N{\fnArial\fs32}- Do you? - What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啦 小盆友 州长不会跟熊孩子住一块的\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'm sorry, little buddy, but governors don't live with bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你个阴险的死叛徒 是我成就了你\N{\fnArial\fs32}You backstabbing turncoat. I made you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malloy 咱俩的关系可得保持低调 就这么个事儿\N{\fnArial\fs32}Malloy, we'll just have to keep our relationship on the down low, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.14,0:11:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们已经开始觉得诡异了\N{\fnArial\fs32}Everybody already thinks it's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诡异? 林肯还跟袋鼠玩过口活\N{\fnArial\fs32}Weird? Lincoln sucked off a kangaroo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好去学下历史\N{\fnArial\fs32}Read a history book.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,综上所述 如果你向往着 各种族和平共处\N{\fnArial\fs32}And so, if you want a state where all races live in peace
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\an8}红肉含有高饱和脂肪 不及其他肉健康
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有战争 没有富人 没有红肉\N{\fnArial\fs32}and harmony without war, rich people, or red meat,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坠胎算是唯一的暴力犯罪\N{\fnArial\fs32}and the only violent acts committed are against unborn babies,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么你们应该选我\N{\fnArial\fs32}you should vote for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺棒的 Ethel\N{\fnArial\fs32}That's great, Ethel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Connie 别捧我 你是来扮演Woody的\N{\fnArial\fs32}Connie, come on. You're supposed to pretend to be Woody.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我忘了\N{\fnArial\fs32}Sorry, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老子是Woody\N{\fnArial\fs32}Argh! I'm Woody!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Connie 你个大傻X 快去摆平那些民兵\N{\fnArial\fs32}Connie, you stupid [Bleep]! Go get rid of that militia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 Woody 他们是我朋友\N{\fnArial\fs32}No, Woody. They're my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你他娘的闭嘴 Connie 你个万人嫌\N{\fnArial\fs32}Shut the hell up, Connie! Everybody hates you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整天又跑又哭的 也不见她瘦点\N{\fnArial\fs32}All that running and crying, you'd think she'd be thinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ethel 你好哇\N{\fnArial\fs32}Ethel! How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 有屁快放 - 我在想啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}- What do you want? - Just thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱俩完全可以做闺蜜呢\N{\fnArial\fs32}I could see us actually becoming pretty good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:12:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那啥 等你当上州长 咱俩一起住官邸的时候\N{\fnArial\fs32}You know, when you're Governor and we're both living at the Governor's mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想跟我一起搬进州长官邸住着?\N{\fnArial\fs32}You want to move into the Governor's mansion with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幻想下 半夜三更咱们穿着睡衣\N{\fnArial\fs32}Think of all the late nights we'd spend in our PJs,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\an8}《恋恋笔记本》男主角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舔着哈根达斯啊 看着Ryan Gosling撸一管啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}binging on Haagen-dazs, rubbing our beavs to Ryan Gosling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白我永远不可能跟你住一起的吧 永远不会\N{\fnArial\fs32}You do realize that there's absolutely no way I'd ever live with you, ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自打我来到这儿 你一直都没让我过个好日子\N{\fnArial\fs32}You've been trying to ruin my life ever since I got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闺蜜你真傻 我都是闹着玩呢亲\N{\fnArial\fs32}Girl, you so crazy. It was all in fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.58,0:12:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的答案是 绝逼不行\N{\fnArial\fs32}The answer is hell no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老子要让你暴尸街头血流满地\N{\fnArial\fs32}The streets will run red with your blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,砖家们说冥王星不再算作行星的时候\N{\fnArial\fs32}So, when they said Pluto was no longer a planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是让我气爆了\N{\fnArial\fs32}well, that really ticked me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我疯了是吧?\N{\fnArial\fs32}Am I crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒没看出来\N{\fnArial\fs32}Not from where I'm sitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道还有谁喜欢冥王星吗? 我妹妹\N{\fnArial\fs32}You know who else likes Pluto? My sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你猜怎么着 大哥?\N{\fnArial\fs32}Guess what, big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咋啦 小妹?\N{\fnArial\fs32}What, little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冥王星不算行星了哟\N{\fnArial\fs32}Pluto's not even a planet anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.02,0:12:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭上你的烂嘴 臭三八\N{\fnArial\fs32}Shut your lying mouth, you bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 兄妹拌嘴嘛\N{\fnArial\fs32}Sorry. Sibling rivalry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她... 看起来是个好人\N{\fnArial\fs32}She... she seems nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我日啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}God damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\an8}"明"兵野餐会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家伙儿 这集会真棒 对吧?\N{\fnArial\fs32}You guys. What a great militia meeting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看咱们的新成员\N{\fnArial\fs32}Look at all these new members.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随便啦 少逼逼 快把民兵奶酪通心粉递过来\N{\fnArial\fs32}Yeah, yeah. Shut your face and pass the militia mac and cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这货是特么谁叫来的?\N{\fnArial\fs32}Who the hell invited this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们绝对反... 反...\N{\fnArial\fs32}We are definitely anti... anti...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是个啥玩艺儿?\N{\fnArial\fs32}What the hell are you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道呀\N{\fnArial\fs32}I have no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就挺不错啦 Bobby\N{\fnArial\fs32}This is awesome, Bobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱的队员人数达到了史上最高\N{\fnArial\fs32}Our membership is at an all-time high.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跨文化兵团是不是感觉高端多了?\N{\fnArial\fs32}And isn't having a multicultural militia so much nicer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想是吧 兵团不是要发表宣言什么的吗?\N{\fnArial\fs32}Yeah, I guess so, but don't militias need to make some sort of statement?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 的确要这样\N{\fnArial\fs32}Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先 民兵是不野餐的\N{\fnArial\fs32}First of all, militias don't have picnics.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那民兵都搞啥啊?\N{\fnArial\fs32}Well, what do militias do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暴动啊 你们怎么可能不知道呢?\N{\fnArial\fs32}Violent acts. How do you not know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们看起来更像少数民族书友会\N{\fnArial\fs32}You guys look more like the Ellis Island Book Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Malloy 你这是干嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs32}Malloy, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 Etheridge战士\N{\fnArial\fs32}Quiet, militia Etheridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让这只说话熊把话说完\N{\fnArial\fs32}Let the talking bear finish talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们想玩真格的\N{\fnArial\fs32}If you want to be a real militia,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须抛头露面做点大事\N{\fnArial\fs32}you need to stand up and do something big,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,具有毁灭性的 可以载入史册的那种大事\N{\fnArial\fs32}something destructive, something that puts you in the history books.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如发明双头震动棒的那货\N{\fnArial\fs32}Like that guy who invented the double-donged dildo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能让他闭嘴吗?\N{\fnArial\fs32}Can he not talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让全世界听到我们声音的时候到了\N{\fnArial\fs32}It's time to make a statement the world will hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没错 算俺们一个 - 好啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}- Hell yeah! Count us in! - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于特么有点民兵的样子了\N{\fnArial\fs32}It's time we started acting like a real [Bleep] militia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\an8}脆莓大讲堂 州长候选人辩论
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\an8}州长候选人辩论赛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\an8}主持人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的孩子考试成绩正在以惊人速度下降\N{\fnArial\fs32}Our children's test scores have been dropping at an alarming rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有何计划呢 Johnson先生?\N{\fnArial\fs32}What is your plan, Mr. Johnson?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 呆逼 这块地盘上只有老子才能提问\N{\fnArial\fs32}Listen, chuckles. I'll be asking the questions around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不行 人家是主持人\N{\fnArial\fs32}No, you won't. He's the moderator.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是喽 老子现在是主持喽\N{\fnArial\fs32}Not anymore. I'm the moderator now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ 我是主持人 欢迎围观 ♪\N{\fnArial\fs32}♪ I'm the moderator, look at me! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ 我是主持人 万人景仰 ♪\N{\fnArial\fs32}♪ Everybody loves me, I'm the moderator! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ 我是主持人 我是主持人 ♪\N{\fnArial\fs32}♪I'm the moderator, I'm the moderator! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ 我就是主持人 ♪\N{\fnArial\fs32}♪I'm the moderator! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面请观众直接发问吧\N{\fnArial\fs32}Let's just take some questions from the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朕许了\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'll allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家好啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hello, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俺是"少数民族书友会兵团"的大首领\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'm the leader of the Ellis Island Book Club militia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俺们决定要刺杀新任州长\N{\fnArial\fs32}And we have decided to assassinate the new Governor,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:15:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以甭管你们谁赢了 都得死\N{\fnArial\fs32}so whichever one of y'all wins, you're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝各位竞选愉快\N{\fnArial\fs32}Y'all have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我听着 我对威胁不予回应\N{\fnArial\fs32}Listen here. I don't respond to threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直都有人告诉我 因为我是个女人 所以应该放弃\N{\fnArial\fs32}All my life, I've been told that because I'm a woman, I should give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听着 我会...\N{\fnArial\fs32}Well guess what! I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将立即退出州长竞选\N{\fnArial\fs32}Dropping out of the race for Governor immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对不对不对 我才会退出竞选\N{\fnArial\fs32}No, no, no, no. I'm dropping out of the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不 是我先退出的\N{\fnArial\fs32}No, you're not! I dropped out first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我比你更有资格退出竞选\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'm much more qualified to drop out of this race than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轮不到你来说 我不能退出竞选\N{\fnArial\fs32}You can't tell me that I can't drop out of this race.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有谁能帮忙叫辆救护车吗?\N{\fnArial\fs32}Would someone please call me an ambulance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天 这家伙问题真特么多\N{\fnArial\fs32}Jesus! This guy asks a lot of [Bleep] questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Malloy? - 干嘛 Connie?\N{\fnArial\fs32}- Uh, Malloy? - Yes, Connie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能加入我们的组织 我真的很高兴 但是...\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'm really happy you joined our militia and everything, but, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉着你那个暗杀州长的主意有些不妥\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'm not so sure about your idea to violently assassinate the Governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心 Connie 不会有人受伤的\N{\fnArial\fs32}Relax, Connie. No one's gonna get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 真的吗? - 真的\N{\fnArial\fs32}- Really? - Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是想吓吓他们 好让他们退出竞选\N{\fnArial\fs32}I just want to scare them into dropping out of the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我不能住进州长官邸 谁也甭想\N{\fnArial\fs32}If I can't live in the Governor's mansion, neither can they.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我 今天没人会死的\N{\fnArial\fs32}Trust me. No one's gonna die today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:16:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天某些人是死定了\N{\fnArial\fs32}Someone's definitely going to die today,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\an8}谁将死?
